  *C102212,1 (Begin) Add HST Tax to the total charge.
  *m.TotalChg = ShipAmt+Freight+Insur+COD+Discount+Tax_Amt+m.nPstAmt
  m.nHstAmt  = IIF(llRate,(ShipAmt+Freight+Insur+COD+;
